com.citytechinc.cq.component.dialog.maker
Class WidgetMakerParameters

java.lang.Object
  com.citytechinc.cq.component.dialog.maker.WidgetMakerParameters

public class WidgetMakerParameters
extends Object

Base parameters which all Widgets use during their creation. This class may be extended to support additional parameters needed for custom widget types.
